    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered every single week. It honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch, dent, or speck of dust anywhere! I'm only parting with it because our family is growing, but it\u2019s a total gem that\u2019s ready for a new home. You won't find another one in this kind of shape!",
