    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Honda S2000 CR is a museum-grade example of the marque\u2019s peak engineering. The F22C1 high-revving power plant features flawless compression across all cylinders, paired with a precision six-speed longitudinal transmission and a factory-spec Torsen helical limited-slip differential. The CR-exclusive suspension geometry, featuring increased spring rates and specialized dampers, remains in factory-fresh condition, offering unparalleled turn-in bite and chassis rigidity thanks to the reinforced X-bone frame. Every aerodynamic component, from the front splitter to the rear wing, is original and free of stress fractures. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a Club Racer with zero mechanical fatigue and a pristine undercarriage.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Zero mechanical issues. Flawless exterior. Interior like new. Maintenance records available. Title in hand.",
      "price": 43000.0,
