    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine example of automotive excellence, maintained to a showroom standard that defines true mint condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a recent professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state\u2014the premium leather is supple and free of wear, the controls are crisp, and it has never been smoked in. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history from day one. Every component functions as it did the day it left the assembly line. All original keys, manuals, and maintenance records are included. For the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality, this car offers a rare 'as-new' driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
