    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and looks practically brand new! No scratches, no dents, and the interior is still spotless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
