    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the zenith of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S65 4.0L V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a cross-plane crankshaft to achieve a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. This unit is mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, providing unparalleled torque vectoring and mechanical grip. The suspension geometry is preserved in its factory-spec configuration, featuring Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and aluminum-intensive multi-link architecture for minimized unsprung mass. Meticulously maintained with preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service already documented, this vehicle offers the precise turn-in and linear power delivery that defined an era. Truly a turn-key collector specimen for the discerning driver.",
